text: Luleå HF is an ice hockey club in the town of Luleå in Sweden. The club was established on 2 May 1977. Luleå HF won the Swedish national championship in 1996 and 2025. It also lost the finals in 1993, 1997 and 2013. ==References== ==Other websites== * Official website Category:Ice hockey teams in Sweden Category:1977 establishments in Sweden Category:Sport in Luleå
